{"tid":2139658,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多棲發展】撐港視被封港版半澤直樹","createTime":"2020-08-04T12:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T14:11:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d33d36e6715e0d482158882c5ca1ea6bcd999dc3","tid":2139658,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:17:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200804/KTTQHDFHCBEBGQY5BACQBK6LSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200804%2FKTTQHDFHCBEBGQY5BACQBK6LSE%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd%2Bf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=81e17932\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200804%2FKTTQHDFHCBEBGQY5BACQBK6LSE%2F&h=8de162a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200804/KTTQHDFHCBEBGQY5BACQBK6LSE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【多棲發展】撐港視被封港版半澤直樹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZyND6HlILZ0-KxI6N88upU0rOrA=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T75CWE5APRS6QCLSTVTL5D7ZTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZyND6HlILZ0-KxI6N88upU0rOrA%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT75CWE5APRS6QCLSTVTL5D7ZTY.jpg&h=841a89d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2013年港視不獲發牌，陸駿光（右）與高俊文等在政總演出港版短劇，被喻為港版半澤直樹。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n42歲的陸駿光於香港演藝學院畢業，2002年簽約無綫，拍過逾70齣劇集，演出多以閒角為主。2012年轉投香港電視，三年間拍了《導火新聞線》、《大眾情性》等劇集，演技令人眼前一亮。惟2013年港視不獲發牌，藝員張松枝、郭鋒、陸駿光和高俊文在政總演出港版短劇《半澤直樹》，諷刺政府黑箱作業，陸駿光飾演「半澤直樹」極為神似，被喻為港版半澤直樹，人氣急升。<br />\n<br />\n其後，陸駿光轉戰影壇，拍過電影《S風暴》、《L風暴》等，於去年《G殺》擔正男主角。近年除主力接拍港台劇外，亦有參演ViuTV劇集《Plan B》及《歎息橋》等。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t0bm7Wz526YtLvjoatgMAsvFdN4=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IVI2LXINNRS6UI2XGMN7IQMBQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft0bm7Wz526YtLvjoatgMAsvFdN4%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIVI2LXINNRS6UI2XGMN7IQMBQI.jpg&h=401fc1dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陸駿光（左）在無綫當藝員，大多數只當閒角，最後拍罷《潛行追擊》就離開無綫。劇照"},{"pid":"9fcd2b8732fe64330b374d56568c71d4f6be839c","tid":2139658,"uid":104769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hroq64h65Os\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHroq64h65Os&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd%2Bf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=03c05dcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hroq64h65Os</a>"}]}